Description_lang: Fleshcraft's passive effect reduces the cooldown by an additional ${$s1/1000} sec when it consumes a corpse.

description_blz.en_US: Fleshcraft's passive effect reduces the cooldown by an additional 1 sec when it consumes a corpse.
